This is a placeholder file for the Excel quiz template.
The actual Excel file should be created by the user with the following format:

Column Headers (Row 1):
- title: Quiz title
- description: Quiz description  
- duration: Duration in minutes

Questions (Rows 2 onwards):
- question: The question text
- option1: First option
- option2: Second option
- option3: Third option
- option4: Fourth option
- correctAnswer: Number of correct option (1, 2, 3, or 4)
